 ### Mode Options
 
-| Mode | Description | Required Fields |
-|------|-------------|-----------------|
-| `azure` | Azure OpenAI Embeddings | `azure.endpoint`, `azure.api_key` |
-| `openai_compatible` | OpenAI-compatible API | Depends on provider |
